title: Rob Zombie's Halloween: The GasmaskAvenger Edition (Version 1.5)
description:
Preview: http://i.imgur.com/ZU1J271.jpg



Original release years of the movies used: 2007 & 2009.

First version of the GasmaskAvenger Edition released in late 2010.

Second version released sometime in 2011.



Starring Malcolm McDowell, Tyler Mane and Scout-Taylor Compton.

Directed By Rob Zombie



This is a reupload of my preferred cut of the acclaimed Rob Zombie Halloween movies fan edit.

If you're only familiar with the shorter first cut of the movie, there's a few new stuff thrown in here and there and since it's been a while since the fall of demonoid, there's really no need for an introduction of this edit, since the first version is surprisingly still available on TPB.


200 minutes long total.
